    <item>
      <title>美国比特币 ETF 流入量创历史新高，代币流入量接近历史最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-bitcoin-btc-etfs-get-third-highest-inflow-with-token-near-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人们对美国大选结果的猜测不断升温的背景下，比特币价格接近历史新高，投资于比特币的美国交易所交易基金净流入 8.7 亿美元，为该基金单日流入量第三高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-bitcoin-btc-etfs-get-third-highest-inflow-with-token-near-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>腾讯支持的 Airwallex 寻求融资，估值达 60 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/tencent-backed-airwallex-seeks-funding-eyes-6-billion-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，企业支付服务提供商 Airwallex 正在与投资者洽谈在新一轮融资中筹集约 2 亿美元以资助其增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/tencent-backed-airwallex-seeks-funding-eyes-6-billion-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰田在日本和中国销量下降，而混合动力车在美国销量增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/toyota-sales-fall-in-japan-china-as-hybrids-make-gains-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管北美对混合动力汽车的需求强劲，但丰田汽车公司在日本和中国的销售仍面临一系列挑战，包括来自电动汽车品牌的竞争加剧、国内丑闻以及海外召回事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/toyota-sales-fall-in-japan-china-as-hybrids-make-gains-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 04:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
